### pip install

#### PyPI

The {{packageName}} is available to be downloaded via PyPI, you can install directly using:

```sh
pip install {{packageName}}
```
(you may need to run `pip` with root permission: `sudo pip install {{packageName}}`)

Then import the package:
```python
import {{{packageName}}}
```

